    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1907-08-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1907-08-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="150"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d150">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 4992/10–11.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Minister <persName type="to">Rockhill</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1907-08-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 13, 1907</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 344.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Referring to your Nos. 563, of March 20, and 571,
                    of March 27 last, in regard to the extradition of Horace G. McKinley from China,
                    I inclose the evidence in the case and the record of his indictment and
                    conviction in the United States district court for the district of Oregon, both
                    duly certified; also copy of a photograph of the fugitive.<note n="1"
                        xml:id="d150fn1">Not printed.</note>
                </p>
                <p>You will take the proper steps to obtain the provisional arrest and detention of
                    McKinley with a view to his extradition for conspiracy to defraud.</p>
                <p>You will telegraph the department upon receipt of information that the fugitive
                    has been arrested.</p>
                <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Alvey A. Adee.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
